That depends on who you think the competition
is ?. Is it an all electric vehicle, like

00:03:46.680 --> 00:03:47.740
the Nissan Leaf?

00:03:47.740 --> 00:03:52.569
Well, I think, it's clearly better from both
the standpoint of its looks which is more

00:03:52.569 --> 00:03:56.740
dad friendly and the performance because of
the range extending gas engine.

00:03:56.740 --> 00:03:58.650
But, is that really the competition?

